<HEADLINE> Lineup For Sunday's News Shows  </HEADLINE>
By The Associated Press	   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Lineup for the Sunday TV news shows:
</P>
<P>
   ABC's ''This Week'' -- Topics: Gore's problems, Jesse Ventura and
the death penalty. Sen. Arlen Specter, R-Pa.; Reps. Dan Burton,
R-Ind., and Barney Frank, D-Mass.; Minnesota Gov. Jesse Ventura and
Rev. Pat Robertson of the Christian Coalition.
</P>
