   CBS' ''Face the Nation'' -- Topics: The death penalty and Social
Security. Guests: Rev. Jesse Jackson, Rep. Asa Hutchinson, R-Ark.;
Sen. Phil Gramm, R-Texas; and Gore adviser Laura D'Andrea Tyson.
</P>
