presidential candidate Ralph Nader and Rev. Pat Robertson of the
Christian Coalition.
</P>
<P>
   ''Fox News Sunday'' -- Topics: Volunteerism, America's youth,
presidential politics, gasoline prices and the Gore fund-raising
investigation. Guests: Colin Powell, chairman of America's Promise;
Sens. Kay Bailey Hutchison, R-Texas, and Tom Harkin, D-Iowa;
Charles LaBella, former Justice Department Campaign Finance Task
Force leader.
</P>
