Giants Defeat Astros 13-4
</SUBHEAD>
<P>
   HOUSTON (AP) - Jeff Kent had four hits, including two in San Francisco's
seven-run third inning, and Doug Mirabelli had a career-high five hits as the
Giants routed the Houston Astros 13-4 today. San Francisco had 22 hits, its
highest total since June 12, 1999.
</P>
