<TEXT>
<P>
   CLEVELAND (AP) -- Bobby Higginson's third homer of the game
brought Detroit all the way back from a seven-run deficit Saturday
night and gave the Tigers an 8-7 lead over the Cleveland Indians in
the second game of day-night doubleheader.
</P>
